snippet.textDisplay: Two player adventure mode made this game amazing. The VS mode was great too. I always used this game to settle disputes over who was the best at kart racers. The lack of rubber band AI and good item gifts to bad drivers made this a more "pure" game to me. If you suck at this game, you will be lapped. That just doesn't happen in Mario Kart.

snippet.textDisplay: Hey SD, I was wondering if you had heard of a game called Thrid Blade? I've been playing it the last few days, pretty addiciting. This is the song I wanted you to hear because I think you would like it.
